<plot>Two high tech salesmen, Savas and Mitsaras go about promoting the new KONY gadget, Sitman. The machine's unique cross-breed qualities allows the viewer both interaction and cyber-transportation of his thoughts and feelings on to what he sees and hears. When sitman is tried out for the very first time by a candidate viewer called Fotis, a middle aged wealthy businessman who liked to keep himself to himself, he takes off on a multi-route journey through the film itself.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?296592</url></doc>
